categories: Category:Unidentified members of the Ohnaka Gang

nodes.text: This pirate was a member of the Ohnaka Gang during the Clone Wars. At some point, General Grievous invaded Florrum for revenge against Hondo Ohnaka, who had held Count Dooku captive. This pirate ran to the dining hall, desperately attempting to warn the pirate leader that they were under attack, however the pirate was killed before he could finish.
